'''Pirates''' are [[monster]]s found in the [[Asgarnia Ice dungeon]], the [[Wilderness]] in [[Pirates' Hideout]], and the [[Brimhaven]] pub.

==Location==
*[[Asgarnia Ice dungeon]]
*[[Pirates' Hideout]]
*[[Dead Man's Chest]]

